item.title: Re: BvS Uzuki ALERT
item.content:encoded: Do you have the Summoning Circle upgrade in your village? If you have that, you will see another button option in your main page. It is under the Learn a Jutsu button. Go their and you will see the summons that you can tame. The requirement to summon is the trainer and you must have at least 300 FPs with that trainer.
